With its eggshell white dial, minimalistic case and elegant light brown leather strap, made from American leather, the Classic Durham is a stunning addition to the flagship Classic collection. The ultra-thin (6mm) watch is suitable for every occasion, and is available in both rose gold and silver.

The Durham leather strap is made of genuine American leather, and has been treated with vegetable oil.&nbsp;Due to the nature of oily leather, the strap will lighten in color when bent or stretched.&nbsp;

The strap color may vary, and variations in grain, texture and natural markings are not considered defects. Daily activities including sun exposure, handling, water, and conditioning will aid this natural process.

